prompts.frontCover: A charming and clumsy cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, lopsided party hat, hanging upside down from a single, gracefully painted tree branch. The sloth is joyfully attempting to juggle three colorful, wobbly birthday cupcakes, with one cupcake hilariously frozen mid-air, about to fall. Below the branch, the greeting "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft, flowing pastel colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the sloth and cupcakes.
